org.semanticweb.owlapi.vocab

Enum OWL2Datatype

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OWL2Datatype>
      • org.semanticweb.owlapi.vocab.OWL2Datatype
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<OWL2Datatype>, HasIRI, HasPrefixedName, HasShortForm

    public enum OWL2Datatype
extends Enum<OWL2Datatype>
implements HasIRI, HasShortForm, HasPrefixedName
    An enumeration of the datatypes in the OWL 2 specification. These are the datatypes in the OWL 2 datatype map.
    Author:
    Matthew Horridge, The University Of Manchester, Information Management Group, Date: 11-Nov-2008
